          <p style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.2; color: #A9A7AF;"><i> The Kurdish militant group said it was "close to completing its historic mission" after decades of conflict with Turkey. Credits: NAZEER AL-KHATIB/AFP via Getty Images</i></p>
